OL,3,CNew Wales head coach is Steve Tandy,
OL,4,CWRU announce
OL,6,FSteve Tandy has been appointed as
OL,7,FWales' new head coach, the Welsh Rugby
OL,8,FUnion has announced.
OL,10,FThe 45-year-old Welshman will become
OL,11,Fthe permanent successor to Warren
OL,12,FGatland on 1 September following
OL,13,Falmost six years as Scotland's defence
OL,14,Fcoach.
OL,16,FTandy is tasked with reviving his
OL,17,Fcountry's fortunes after the side's
OL,18,Frecord 18-match losing run finally
OL,19,Fended on 12 July with a 31-22 victory
OL,20,Fover Japan in Kobe.
