OL,3,CNew Wales head coach is Steve Tandy,
OL,4,CWRU announce
OL,6,FHis first match in charge will be on
OL,7,FSunday, 9 November, against Argentina
OL,8,Fin Cardiff, which will be followed by
OL,9,Fmeetings with Japan, New Zealand, and
OL,10,Fworld champions South Africa on the
OL,11,Ffollowing three weekends.
OL,13,F"Becoming head coach of my home
OL,14,Fcountry is a massive honour and a
OL,15,Fprivilege," said Tandy, who will lead
OL,16,FWales into the 2027 Rugby World Cup in
OL,17,FAustralia.
