OL,3,CNew Wales head coach is Steve Tandy,
OL,4,CWRU announce
OL,6,F"I am looking forward to playing a
OL,7,Frole in the rebuilding phase of Welsh
OL,8,Frugby and taking the national team
OL,9,Fback to competing with the best
OL,10,Fcountries in the world.
OL,12,F"I am excited about the potential of
OL,13,FWelsh rugby and the group of young,
OL,14,Fhardworking players we have."
OL,16,FGatland's second spell as Wales boss
OL,17,Fended in February on the back of a 22-
OL,18,F15 defeat to Italy in the second round
OL,19,Fof this year's Six Nations.
