OL,3,CNew Wales head coach is Steve Tandy,
OL,4,CWRU announce
OL,6,FMatt Sherratt took over on a temporary
OL,7,Fbasis and oversaw defeats to Ireland,
OL,8,FScotland and England before leading
OL,9,Fthis summer's two-match tour of Japan,
OL,10,Fwhich began on 5 July with a 24-19
OL,11,Floss in Kitakyushu.
OL,13,FTonmawr-born Tandy was head coach of
OL,14,FOspreys between 2012 and 2018, which
OL,15,Fincluded winning the PRO12 title in
OL,16,Fhis first season, before serving as
OL,17,Fdefence coach for Australian side the
OL,18,FWaratahs.
